# for ALL Uranium maps is a BUILD_PLAN follow-up; the pathfinder slice paths are
# listed explicitly for now. The assembler NO LONGER edits tracked upstream files in
# place: data/event_scripts.s + map_data_rules.mk carry committed, stable include-hooks
# and all per-slice content lands in the generated *.gen.json / *.inc files below.
# See engine/RPG2GBA_VENDOR.md.
